      • compareByLabel

        public static int compareByLabel(IComponent<?> c1,
                                 IComponent<?> c2)
        Compares the two specified terminology independent component's label lexicographically, ignoring case differences. The sign of the value returned is the same as that of c1.getLabel().compareToIgnoreCase(c2.getLabel()).
        Parameters:
        c1 - the first IComponent to compare
        c2 - the second IComponent to compare
        Returns:
        a negative integer, zero, or a positive integer as the specified label is greater than, equal to, or less than this component label, ignoring case considerations.
